name: Graphite Pencils x Geometric Art Style

metadata.name: HONESTY
metadata.description:
"Honesty is often rough, painful, and bloody. But with honesty, you can find the truth, trust, and beautiful light even in the darkness."

Graphite Pencils x Digital Arts

Tools of traditional art:  
Paper A3 (30 cm x 40 cm)  
Graphite Pencils (2B, 4B, 8B)  
Mechanical Eraser  
Brush  
Paper Stump

The result of traditional art was combined with manual digital art.

3000 x 4000 px
